Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.78,0:00:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最開始發現事端的是小孩子們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.70,0:00:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等 力高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.37,0:00:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.16,0:00:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是迷路了 挨罵的可是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.13,0:00:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一直說不要再森林裡擅自行動嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.80,0:00:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要讓狼吃了我可不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.42,0:00:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算沒狼最近還有庫夏人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.88,0:00:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖精
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.80,0:00:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.76,0:00:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 看見妖精了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.60,0:00:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你胡說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.26,0:00:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說我才討厭帶這個小鬼一起出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.56,0:00:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手吧 杜馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.27,0:00:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是力高那種感覺 我也能理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.82,0:00:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢 最近總是感覺怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.74,0:00:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 你也這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.99,0:00:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 對啊 我也這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.74,0:00:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.41,0:00:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們從之前開始就經常來這個叢林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.12,0:00:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.16,0:00:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.41,0:00:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 怎麼說簡直就像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.29,0:00:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像夢中森林一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.25,0:01:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才聽到什麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.63,0:01:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.64,0:01:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.60,0:01:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次又是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.98,0:01:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.94,0:01:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 森林裡的魔物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.32,0:01:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪獸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.69,0:01:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.07,0:01:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樹木的小洞 草葉的陰影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.70,0:01:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波浪的空隙 風的細語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.70,0:01:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古井的底部 屋簷下的暗處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.92,0:01:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在不知不覺的暗地裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.09,0:01:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉默變得不再沉默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.80,0:01:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像老人對小孩子說的故事般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.22,0:01:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像從前就一直存在一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.14,0:02:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在沉默之中 的確有東西在蠹蠢欲動
Comment: Marked=0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,/--------START---------/
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.58,0:03:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.30,0:03:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯 卡嘉姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.52,0:04:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是晚了一步啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.28,0:04:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯離開之後不久就去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.90,0:04:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.11,0:04:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 爸爸說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.78,0:04:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在垂死之際遇見你就很幸運了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.62,0:04:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也不想讓格斯看到自己的死相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.46,0:04:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真的太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.21,0:04:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了卡思嘉姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.29,0:04:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是就那麼失蹤了 就全是我的錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.46,0:04:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來格斯要幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.59,0:04:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會又把姐姐丟下不管吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡一起生活吧 大家一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.56,0:04:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯也在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.98,0:04:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精心照料的話 姐姐一定也不會逃跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.24,0:04:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.32,0:04:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎 真是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.45,0:04:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約好了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.79,0:05:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.50,0:05:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼輕易的回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.79,0:05:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我也還差著火候呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.75,0:05:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把卡思嘉救回來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.84,0:05:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 當我為了救她而揮起劍的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.22,0:05:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.39,0:05:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現在我面前的不是魔物 而是人的形態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.52,0:05:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像把那個時候完全呈現出來一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.82,0:05:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到他的瞬間 忘記了殺意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.99,0:05:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點不可原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.74,0:05:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是沒有目的的旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.54,0:05:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅憑著些許怪異的傳言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.66,0:05:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和靠著微弱的烙印的感知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哪裡都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.75,0:05:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那傢伙根本不在這個世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.09,0:05:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為了追蹤他的影子而劈開死靈流浪至今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.97,0:06:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在 他和我同在一個世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.43,0:06:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腳下踏的是同樣的大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.35,0:06:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的劍尖能觸及的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.56,0:06:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 現在家裡有客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.57,0:06:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.53,0:06:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說是里基特的老朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.82,0:06:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是部對裡的老朋友 格斯會不會也認識呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.83,0:06:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有著一頭白銀色的長髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.62,0:06:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人想不到是男人般非常的漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.71,0:06:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺就像童話故事中的人一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.18,0:06:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的還難以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.93,0:06:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天格斯和卡思嘉之外就沒人再回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.23,0:06:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捷度 哥爾卡斯 比賓 大家都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.86,0:06:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道那天發生了什度事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.45,0:07:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯也不和我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.74,0:07:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為全部 全部都已經完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.62,0:07:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還能像這樣見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.79,0:07:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.51,0:07:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.27,0:07:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.27,0:07:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲開 里基特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.85,0:07:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不躲開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.98,0:07:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就要砍過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.90,0:07:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 格里弗斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.36,0:07:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的 那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.69,0:07:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格里弗斯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.44,0:07:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.74,0:07:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那已經不是你認識的格里弗斯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.49,0:07:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.25,0:07:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊躲開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.58,0:07:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不躲 我搞不懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.71,0:07:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有變啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.88,0:07:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動嘴之前先動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.55,0:08:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不如說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.63,0:08:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要用同樣的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.84,0:08:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和第一次見你的時候一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.76,0:08:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要用同樣的笑容 同樣的聳意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.02,0:08:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說我的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.06,0:08:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是來幹什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.56,0:08:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來見你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.61,0:08:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個塔裡相當的亂啊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.15,0:08:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒找到和你們倆說話的時機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.12,0:08:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個地方很合適吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.33,0:08:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們鷹之團的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.87,0:08:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次集結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.25,0:08:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要從你嘴裡說出那個詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.04,0:08:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來確認一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.05,0:08:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以這個新的肉體出現在你面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.80,0:08:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會有什麼能令你的內心動搖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.35,0:08:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來 我已經 自由了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.10,0:08:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.48,0:08:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對你做過的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.31,0:09:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對你背叛過的那些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.65,0:09:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點感覺都沒有嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.57,0:09:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法背叛我的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.28,0:09:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.75,0:09:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見啊 黑色劍士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.21,0:09:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.47,0:09:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 卡思嘉姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.56,0:09:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個氣息是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擋住了格斯大劍的一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擋住了格斯大劍的一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男人到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.12,0:09:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然打破我的預言 活到了現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.04,0:09:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高興啊 小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.98,0:10:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好劍法 竟憑人類之身能鍛鍊到這種地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.44,0:10:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早想用這幅形態和從戰場上生還的你打一場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.07,0:10:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.12,0:10:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什度你會和格里弗斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.58,0:10:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我躲開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找格里弗斯有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.00,0:10:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多說無用 打倒我再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何等的劍壓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.55,0:10:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是接不住的話 挨一擊就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.98,0:11:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍有鬆懈 頭顱就會被砍下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.36,0:11:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是招架而已 骨頭就要斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.32,0:11:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是我能接住的劍壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.57,0:11:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還能一戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.24,0:11:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了接近他的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在數不盡的夜晚 我一直在戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.99,0:11:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好礙事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.24,0:11:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.87,0:11:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種戰鬥 在戰場可沒有見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.75,0:11:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯變強了 強到無法想像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟能把大劍使得那樣純熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.47,0:11:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那股憤怒和怨念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.18,0:11:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是衝著格里弗斯去的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.51,0:11:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.47,0:11:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.31,0:11:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.45,0:11:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼戰鬥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.66,0:11:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男人也很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.71,0:12:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯那敏捷的判斷力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.17,0:12:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死戰 格斯經歷過怎樣難以想像的死戰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.22,0:12:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的血應該已經凍住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.14,0:12:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是作為我的容器的融合在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.14,0:12:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個嬰兒的記憶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.07,0:12:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好劍法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.61,0:12:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以人類之身從蝕之刻生還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.66,0:12:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和在使徒戰鬥中磨練的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.16,0:12:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來從庫夏人那裡搶來的斬馬刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.92,0:12:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點配不上你的那把斬魔刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.30,0:12:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出色的劍 出色的招數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.88,0:12:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝負從這裡開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.72,0:12:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒享受夠啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.60,0:13:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒吃夠啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.60,0:13:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.31,0:13:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有錯 那個男人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.32,0:13:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不死的佐德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.32,0:13:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.15,0:13:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.15,0:13:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 高特大叔的礦洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.62,0:14:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 卡思嘉姐姐你又到處亂跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.79,0:14:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 不要過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.63,0:14:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯 剛才好像有很大的聲意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.74,0:14:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怪獸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.41,0:14:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.83,0:14:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.17,0:14:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.91,0:15:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.79,0:15:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了 回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.60,0:15:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你要去哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.35,0:15:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.81,0:15:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要得到自己的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.23,0:15:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有一點變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.16,0:16:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里基特 什麼都沒有結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.62,0:16:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道真相後 就算恨我也沒有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.08,0:16:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是即使那樣 也要追求夢想的延續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.67,0:16:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就沒有理由去拒絶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.72,0:16:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊 我不明白啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.22,0:16:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相到底是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.94,0:16:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 格斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.69,0:16:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲開 里基特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.48,0:16:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼都沒有改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.23,0:16:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做過哪些事後 還什麼都沒有改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.57,0:16:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.99,0:16:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是那樣的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.62,0:16:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你最清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.79,0:17:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯 也告訴我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.13,0:17:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天格里弗斯和大家到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.51,0:17:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有知曉的懼利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.97,0:17:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不知道不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.72,0:17:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.11,0:17:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.66,0:17:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然 竟然發生那種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.54,0:17:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也隱約察覺到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.46,0:17:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個影像是當時的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.26,0:17:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 全部都被埋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.43,0:17:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊 好不容易和格斯還有卡思嘉姐姐一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.31,0:17:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯你一個人要背負這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.06,0:18:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我卻在這裡舒舒服服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.61,0:18:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶我走啊 我也是鷹之團的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.86,0:18:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.24,0:18:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.20,0:18:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你並沒有憎恨格里弗斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.41,0:18:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都要走嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.04,0:18:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.50,0:18:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊追上去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.55,0:18:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你要怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.22,0:18:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要繼續嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.93,0:18:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復仇之旅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.85,0:18:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再丟下卡思嘉不管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.98,0:18:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道要帶卡思嘉一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.15,0:18:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道那是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.44,0:18:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是精靈礦洞已經塌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.11,0:18:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣留下來就有些勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.66,0:18:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個有烙印的人在一起不會有什麼好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.66,0:18:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在斷罪之塔已經證明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.71,0:19:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近還有精靈的住所嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.58,0:19:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說有也不是沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.59,0:19:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還要把卡思嘉關起來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.55,0:19:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可憐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.59,0:19:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來就是不願意才離家出走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.30,0:19:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就靠精靈的智慧袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.35,0:19:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了 有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.64,0:19:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.52,0:19:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有個大概比哪裡都安全有漂亮的天國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.27,0:19:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.11,0:19:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.92,0:19:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊 救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.26,0:19:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們接下來會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.63,0:19:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽傳言說 厙夏人會把女人作為神的祭品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.68,0:19:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不要那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.06,0:20:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說都完蛋了 這個國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.77,0:20:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是鷹之團在的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.15,0:20:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人要是在的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.06,0:20:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在才說這種話也殳用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.94,0:20:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.86,0:20:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久之後 救贖的手就會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.82,0:20:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什度夢話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.95,0:20:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雙親在眼前被燒死 精神恍惚了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.16,0:20:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會來的 光之鷹會來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.16,0:20:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風是這麼輕聲訴說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.63,0:20:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動員整族人都捉不到一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.09,0:20:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很失望啊! 巴基拉卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.97,0:20:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還聽你說 坐在魔獸上飛走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.68,0:20:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我僭越 這次的行軍就是為了向大神官顯示神蹟才開始的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.69,0:20:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就算有什麼超常的現象也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.57,0:20:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由逆賊組成的奴隸階層的一族算什麼戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.07,0:20:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大帝也是不但把這種垃圾收作士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.37,0:21:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止雜務竟然還委派大任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.83,0:21:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也真是糊塗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.42,0:21:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 你要幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.63,0:21:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事態緊急抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.55,0:21:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.26,0:21:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個畜生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.94,0:21:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我失禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.81,0:21:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼手法 怪物嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.82,0:21:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我們就繼續 「鷹」的搜索了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.67,0:21:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.68,0:23:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要保重啊 不好好保護姐姐可不行啊格斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.02,0:23:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我離開鷹之團的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.56,0:23:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是下著這樣的雪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.78,0:23:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次是我被遺棄了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.45,0:23:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會再丟下你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.33,0:23:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次不會失去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.09,0:24:06.09,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}那間屋子\N我已經不想回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.05,0:24:10.13,Preview,,0,0,0,,欸 奇怪的兔子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.26,0:24:14.43,Preview,,0,0,0,,你的主人是我 是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.51,0:24:18.60,Preview,,0,0,0,,母親大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.64,0:24:22.60,Preview,,0,0,0,,在外面 不這樣生存是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.60,0:02:04.10,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\pos(1000,770)}綻放的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.02,0:24:28.11,Title,,0,0,0,,{\b0\bord0\shad0\pos(972,800)\fs95}冬天的旅行
